Kassandra Tokenomics

What is KSNDR?

KSNDR is a utility token within Kassandra. KSNDR benefits from the speed, scalability, and low cost transactions of the Solana ecosystem as well as transparency and auditability provided by the Blockchain.

What is CRBRL?

CRBRL is an investment token. CRBRL tokens are earned by investing into initial system development and represent a share of the Kassandra evaluation.

During further development of Kassandra, CRBRL will become an option that obliges the exchange of company shares during upcoming investment rounds.

Supply

KSNDR tokens have indefinite supply. Tokens are generated based on Proof of Value where members earn tokens for providing value within Kassandra as defined by the Kassandra Merit system.


CRBRL tokens have limited supply, which will initially be owned by the Kassandra team and proposed to investors in the upcoming two years, before being transferred to shares at the end of that period.

Token Creation

Tokens are created for the following activities:

  • Kassandra Service Usage
  • Hosting Kassandra Services
  • Investing
  • Content Creation
  • Suggestions
  • Development with Kassandra
  • Growing the Kassandra Ecosystem and Membership
Token Destruction

KSNDR tokens are burned (destroyed) when they are used within the Kassandra Governance system. Kassandra Governance allows Kassandra members to vote for changes, make suggestions, and modify the rules of Kassandra Merit and the Kassandra ecosystem in general.
